item.description:
首先让我们看Dispatchers.IO，毫无疑问它创建64个worker
// Dispatchers.IO internal object DefaultIoScheduler : ExecutorCoroutineDispatcher(), Executor { private val default = UnlimitedIoScheduler.limitedParallelism( systemProp( IO_PARALLELISM_PROPERTY_NAME, 64.coerceAtLeast(AVAILABLE_PROCESSORS) ) ) override fun dispatch(context: CoroutineContext, block: Runnable) { default.dispatch(context, block) } } 继续跟进，发现Dispatchers.IO竟然将任务直接提交给Dispatchers.Default
// The unlimited instance of Dispatchers.IO that utilizes all the threads CoroutineScheduler provides private object UnlimitedIoScheduler : CoroutineDispatcher() { ... override fun dispatch(context: CoroutineContext, block: Runnable) { DefaultScheduler.dispatchWithContext(block, BlockingContext, false) } } 接下来是Default，CORE_POOL_SIZE就是CPU核心数，
internal object DefaultScheduler : SchedulerCoroutineDispatcher( CORE_POOL_SIZE, MAX_POOL_SIZE, IDLE_WORKER_KEEP_ALIVE_NS, DEFAULT_SCHEDULER_NAME ) { .
